<p>However, one of these factors may even be more delicate:&#xA0;employee scheduling. Absence requests, timetables, and availability calendars all have to be considered when trying to organize shifts.</p>
<p>Nowadays,&#xA0;scheduling software&#xA0;exists and helps simplify these processes, and in the following, we will have an in-depth look at how&#xA0;retail scheduling&#xA0;works and the problems most&#xA0;retail managers&#xA0;face.</p>
